      "content": "## AI Health Dashboard & Monitoring (Feb 11, 2026 — LIVE)\n- **Route**: `/admin/ai-health` (session-protected) — 10 module cards + 7 AI modality cards + 11 AI module rows + call distribution\n- **Tabs**: Overview (cards), Status (health banner, 12 stat cards, DB pool gauge, slow queries, token budget per-provider, activity feed), Metrics (CPU/memory/DB/API latency percentiles), AI Monitoring (budget predictions, hourly usage chart, model performance, module cost breakdown, real-time call log), Prompts (registry, version history, perf metrics), Activity Feed (60+ route patterns)\n- **Backend collectors**: `db.js` (query tracking, pool %), `metrics-collector.js` (HTTP connections), `token-budget.js` (per-provider), `ai-call-logger.js` (every call: module/provider/model/tokens/latency/cost/fallback)\n- **Budget prediction**: Burn rate calculation, forecasts 100K daily exhaustion time\n- **Priority-based throttling**: Critical modules (interviews, assessments) never throttled; low-priority auto-throttled at 80%+ budget\n- **Prompt management**: Registry, version control, A/B testing, rollback\n- **13 new API endpoints**: `/api/ai-health/usage`, `/api/ai-health/budget`, `/api/ai-health/logs`, `/api/ai-health/models`, `/api/ai-health/failover-stats`, `/api/ai-health/predictions`, `/api/ai-health/prompts`, `/api/ai-health/prompt-versions`, `/api/ai-health/ab-tests`, `/api/ai-health/nq` (natural language query)",
      "relevance": "73%"
    },
    {
      "layer": 1,
      "layer_name": "Domain Knowledge (This Company)",
      "header": "Mock Interview & AI Coaching (Feb 10-11, 2026 — ALL FIXED)",
      "content": "## Mock Interview & AI Coaching (Feb 10-11, 2026 — ALL FIXED)\n- **Flow**: Setup (role + JD) → Interview (AI voice Q&A) → Analysis (video + voice) → History\n- **Questions**: 25 AI-generated role-specific (cached, randomized) | Fallback: 8 scripted | Greeting: \"Alex\" intro + self-intro prompt\n- **Audio Pipeline**: TTS (OpenAI nova + `tts_cache` MP3 by content hash, zero tokens on hit) | Recognition (real-time capture, useRef mirrors prevent stale closure) | Transcription (Whisper WAV/MP3/WebM multipart, with Deepgram fallback) | Silence detection (3.5s auto-next) | Video analysis (frame capture every 5s → GPT-4o vision at END only, requires HTTP URLs not base64) | Voice analysis (tone, pace, clarity, confidence) | Dynamic follow-ups (AI probes vague answers)\n- **Feedback**: Answer Content | Communication & Speech | Body Language + bonus (Arc, trends, per-question STAR, technical depth) | Threshold: 1 candidate turn minimum | Returns `no_feedback` flag on 0 answers\n- **iOS Fixes**: Web Audio API + AudioContext on gesture, `muted`, `playsInline`, `webkit-playsinline=\"\"`, `isolation: isolate` + `overflow-hidden` parent\n- **STALE CLOSURE BUG (FIXED Feb 10)**: useRef mirrors for `mockLiveTranscript`, `voiceMode`, `candidateRecording` — all async callbacks read refs\n- **JSON PARSING BUGS (FIXED Feb 11)**: Voice quality + AI turn generation fragile on raw `JSON.parse` — implemented `safeParseJSON()` with 7 repair strategies (unescaped quotes, trailing commas, truncated arrays, etc.)\n- **Vision timeout (body language) (FIXED Feb 11)**: Bumped from 10s to 30s default; multi-image analysis needs 20-30s",
      "relevance": "72%"
    },
    {
      "layer": 3,
      "layer_name": "Cross-Company Patterns",
      "header": "Current Cross-Company Patterns (engineering) (9847 tokens)",
      "content": "## Current Cross-Company Patterns (engineering) (9847 tokens)",
      "relevance": "41%"
    },
    {
      "layer": 2,
      "layer_name": "Company Context & Preferences",
      "header": "Backend Status",
      "content": "## Backend Status\n- **95%+ functional** — all core workflows + AI agents tested and verified\n- 75+ DB tables, 30-column offers table fully integrated\n- 35+ AI endpoints (candidate + recruiter + matching + memory + OmniScore)\n- Question bank at `/api/recruiter/question-bank` AND `/api/memory/question-bank`\n- **OpenAI token budget: 100K tokens/day hard cap** — auto-failover to NIM models for LLM/Vision/Embeddings\n- **TTS/ASR remain on OpenAI** (use <1% of token budget, exempt from daily limit)\n- **⚠️ KNOWN RISK: NIM audio models not available** — all 7 TTS/ASR endpoints return 404 (NVIDIA cloud doesn't host audio). OpenAI audio has zero fallback\n- **⚠️ AI Interview Flow known issue**: Mock interview can hang after candidate answers — `/mock/voice-respond` endpoint (STT + LLM + TTS chain) may timeout or fail silently; likely culprits: daily token budget exhaustion, JSON parse failures in AI turn generation, endpoint timeout",
      "relevance": "36%"
    },
    {
      "layer": 1,
      "layer_name": "Domain Knowledge (This Company)",
      "header": "AI Integration Status",
      "content": "## AI Integration Status\n- **11 of 16 modules have AI**: Interviews, Jobs, Onboarding, Assessments, Matching, Profiles, Documents, Compliance, Payroll, Analytics, Coaching\n- **AI Proxy**: Anthropic via `POLSIA_API_URL` (text-only, `lib/polsia-ai.js`); OpenAI via `OPENAI_BASE_URL` (vision/multimodal, `polsia.com/ai/openai/v1`)\n- **⚠️ MISSING ENV VAR**: `POLSIA_API_URL` not set → Anthropic client never initializes → OpenAI burns budget faster; set to Polsia Anthropic endpoint URL to restore LLM failover chain\n- **Vision images MUST be HTTP URLs** — base64 returns 500\n- **OpenAI create() MUST include `task` fiel",
      "relevance": "34%"
    }
  ]
}

